The Four Seasons resorts in Portugal and Spain reported a good sales
performance but incurred losses. Good progress was being made in Germany.
The company said it would incur a further loss in the second half but hoped
to return to profit in 1994.
Losses per share amounted to 1.47p (3.31p).
