                  JAPAN'S PAPER AND PULP COMPANIES
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
                         Sales      Change    Pre-tax     Change
                         Y(bn)         %       profit        %
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Nippon                   318.52     -21.0       4.03       -21.0
Daishowa                 144.90      -8.7     -11.41           -
Honshu                    185.8      -5.7       3.5         33.6
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
